<pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/china-creates-230-bln-brokerage-powerhouse-consolidation-gathers-pace-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾前市长郭爱丽从印度尼西亚被驱逐后抵达马尼拉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-ex-mayor-alice-guo-arrives-manila-after-deportation-indonesia-2024-09-06/</link><description>菲律宾前市长郭爱丽被指控与中国犯罪集团有联系并洗钱超过 1 亿比索（179 万美元），她在被印度尼西亚驱逐​​出境后于周五早些时候抵达马尼拉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 01:52:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-ex-mayor-alice-guo-arrives-manila-after-deportation-indonesia-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>超强台风“八木”登陆华南地区，导致学校停课、航班取消</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/super-typhoon-yagi-slams-southern-china-shutting-schools-cancelling-flights-2024-09-06/</link><description>周五，超强台风八木带来的强风和暴雨袭击了中国南部地区，学校连续第二天停课，航班取消，这是今年袭击亚洲的最强风暴之一，即将登陆海南热带海岸。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 00:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/super-typhoon-yagi-slams-southern-china-shutting-schools-cancelling-flights-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：动荡的一周紧张结束，日元有望突破</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国和中国指挥官将在“未来几周”讨论预防冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-commanders-discuss-conflict-prevention-in-next-few-weeks-2024-09-05/</link><description>美国驻华大使周四表示，驻印太美军司令将在未来几周内与中国武装部队南部战区司令进行通话，目的是防止超级大国之间出现任何军事误解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:41:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-commanders-discuss-conflict-prevention-in-next-few-weeks-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国担心日本竞购美国钢铁公司可能会影响重要的钢铁供应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/us-worries-about-steel-supply-infrastructure-after-nippon-us-steel-deal-2024-09-05/</link><description>路透社看到，美国在发给美国钢铁公司的一封信中表示，新日铁拟以 149 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的提议将带来国家安全风险，因为这可能会损害关键运输、建筑和农业项目所需的钢铁供应。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:33:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/us-worries-about-steel-supply-infrastructure-after-nippon-us-steel-deal-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>万豪表示大中华区预订窗口缩短至三天以内</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriott-says-booking-window-greater-china-down-under-three-days-2024-09-05/</link><description>酒店运营商万豪国际集团周四表示，大中华区的一项关键预订指标目前还不到三天，在全球第二大经济体的不确定性不断上升的情况下，人们对旅行计划更加谨慎。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriott-says-booking-window-greater-china-down-under-three-days-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦警告终止美国清洁能源税收抵免将增加消费者成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/yellen-warns-that-ending-us-clean-energy-tax-credits-would-raise-consumer-costs-2024-09-05/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四警告称，任何取消拜登政府清洁能源税收抵免的企图都会增加家庭成本，并危及正在创造就业机会的美国制造业的新投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/yellen-warns-that-ending-us-clean-energy-tax-credits-would-raise-consumer-costs-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>南非总统称中国不会将非洲推入债务陷阱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</link><description>南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨周四表示，他不认为中国在非洲的投资会将非洲大陆推入“债务陷阱”，而是互利关系的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国与国际合作伙伴一起对先进技术实施新的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-implements-new-controls-advanced-technology-alongside-international-partners-2024-09-05/</link><description>美国周四根据国际合作伙伴施加的限制，发布了对包括量子计算机在内的先进技术的新控制措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 13:30:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-implements-new-controls-advanced-technology-alongside-international-partners-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲奢侈品股因中国担忧而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-luxury-stocks-drop-china-concerns-2024-09-05/</link><description>欧洲一些大型奢侈品公司的股价周四大幅下跌，交易员称，在世界第二大经济体出现疲软的最新迹象后，人们越来越担心中国主要市场的需求放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 12:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-luxury-stocks-drop-china-concerns-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>《资本》报道，德国正在起草针对中国在线折扣店的法规</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/germany-drafting-regulations-chinese-online-discounters-capital-reports-2024-09-05/</link><description>据《资本》杂志报道，德国正在起草新法规，以确保 Temu 和 Shein 等中国折扣零售商遵守产品安全、环境保护、消费者权利以及海关和税法标准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/germany-drafting-regulations-chinese-online-discounters-capital-reports-2024-09-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>